VhDir Primary Source Push

This value set defines a set of codes that indicate if a primary source of validated data has the capacity to send validation details directly to a validated healthcare directory.

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include these codes as defined in http://hl7.org/fhir/ig/vhdir/CodeSystem/codesystem-validation
    CodeDisplay
    yesyesyes
    nonono
    undeterminedUndeterminedThe validation process is complete and a determination could not be made that the the attested data is, or is not, true and accurate.
